{"tid":1572132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實戰爭中最有效嘅唔係殲敵，係令致敵軍嚴重受傷而死唔去","createTime":"2019-09-15T15:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T23:17:09.000Z","uid":78769,"like":76,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7206de107080ae6b744562f4879ffabed4283ccb","tid":1572132,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:06:58.000Z","msg":"依個係增加敵軍成本同代價比較有效嘅方法。<br />\n<br />\n實際就係令到佢失去作戰能力，傷殘（e.g. 斷手斷腳），尤其是好返之後健健康康但要人養要人照顧。<br />\n<br />\n所以點解會有人轉揀手手腳腳，就係知你唔死重大鑊，可能成世傷殘要人照顧；喺戰略上係一個好重大嘅進取。<br />\n<br />\n因此打死人唔係最有效嘅方式，令致其永久傷殘，失去作戰能力先最係上策。<br />\n<br />\nO, 我其實係講梗美軍喺中東到打仗比人炸到斷手斷腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49d69b6f6333c7686a70874b08caca8430b5857","tid":1572132,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:07:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"1839a5657e01cded25011a9ea27aec448b30696a","tid":1572132,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:07:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5df5e98bdc823da03ca3e5c411d57ad772aa48f6","tid":1572132,"uid":78769,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:18:52.000Z","msg":"呀，唔幾得講下實例，比如係反人員地雷（e.g. BLU-43 Dragontooth, 好細舊, 喺越戰用過）其實唔係想攞人命，係想炸斷啲腳，又死唔去，除非你啲軍隊咁恨心唔理傷兵，如果唔係一個傷咗就可能要幾個去care同埋保護，所以殲滅的而且確唔係上策<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位參與依場學術討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9693f1a17aecac4f29c7dece9d340bbb02da2e68","tid":1572132,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:19:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e914a416117198b285d912279f124ddc69aa677","tid":1572132,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:34:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f0b793cf0b6e795cb8b0d0328464a468a5a1767","tid":1572132,"uid":169074,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:35:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7dbcf71649faa02f2f4e44ac40b2c227b6e5763d","tid":1572132,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f0b793cf0b6e795cb8b0d0328464a468a5a1767","tid":1572132,"uid":169074,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:35:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:38:15.000Z","msg":"其實唔難諗，係一啲好基礎嘅軍事常識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8562928294c4834a8874dbee745f542bbd27f3d","tid":1572132,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:39:05.000Z","msg":"前設係啲士兵唔係condom"},{"pid":"5dab9f8737096b6110c7470be0401666fc894a18","tid":1572132,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:39:15.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n[品葱轉載] [文宣戰術] 教你如何宣傳反共，緊貼現在熱門事件。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1572207\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1572207</a>"},{"pid":"ae562636a921810631bf721d3cf31c66c24def27","tid":1572132,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8562928294c4834a8874dbee745f542bbd27f3d","tid":1572132,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:39:05.000Z","msg":"前設係啲士兵唔係condom"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:43:54.000Z","msg":"冇錯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過如果啲兵仔係condom 咁枝軍隊嘅團結度、組織力同埋士氣都唔慌高得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除非好似中東嗰啲人肉炸彈一嚟就諗住同你一鑊熟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca7eab5503496e3ca594a598560b185bf7a69080","tid":1572132,"uid":211469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:44:53.000Z","msg":"推!!"},{"pid":"3af4c4b0abf04ed3768f6b5c34efedb21449b065","tid":1572132,"uid"